         "__identifier": "Lines",
         "__type": "Array<String>",
         "__value": [
          "My herb bed's gone to dust, friend - and no sword fixes that.",
          "If something could coax green from dead ground, the grove's",
          "small folk would eat this winter. The bed is right here beside me."
         ],
